      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Wavering Moon and Thunder",
        "Client": "Well-dressed Youth",
        "Description": "My guards have turned craven\r\nafter hearing of a Zinogre in\r\nthe area. Nonetheless, I must\r\npress on through the Forest,\r\nno matter what... Which is why\r\nI implore you, brave Hunter,\r\nto vanquish the beast instead.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Lune vacillante et tonnerre",
        "Client": "Jeune bien habill\u00E9",
        "Description": "Depuis qu\u0027ils ont entendu\r\nparler du Zinogre qui tra\u00EEne\r\npar ici, mes gardes ont pris\r\nla fuite... Mais il faut que\r\nj\u0027avance ! Alors si tu pouvais\r\nt\u0027occuper de ce monstre\r\n\u00E0 notre place...",
        "Target": "Chasser un Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Luna e tuono tremanti",
        "Client": "Giovane ben vestito",
        "Description": "Le mie guardie sono scappate\r\nquando hanno saputo che c\u0027\u00E8\r\nuno Zinogre in zona. Io, per\u00F2,\r\ndevo assolutamente\r\nattraversare la foresta!\r\nTi scongiuro, sconfiggi\r\nquella bestia!",
        "Target": "Caccia uno Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Unstet wie Mond und Donner",
        "Client": "Gut gekleideter J\u00FCngling",
        "Description": "Meine Wachen sind desertiert,\r\nals sie von einem Zinogre hier\r\nin der Gegend geh\u00F6rt haben.\r\nIch muss aber durch den Wald,\r\nkoste es, was es wolle... Also\r\nbitte ich dich, mir die Bestie\r\naus dem Weg zu schaffen.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Zinogre.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Trueno y luna vacilante",
        "Client": "Joven bien vestido",
        "Description": "Mis guardias se han amilanado\r\ntras o\u00EDr que hay un Zinogre en\r\nla zona, \u00A1pero tenemos que\r\natravesar el bosque cueste lo\r\nque cueste! Te ruego que\r\nderrotes a esa bestia.",
        "Target": "Caza un Zinogre",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041A\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0431\u043B\u044E\u0449\u0430\u044F\u0441\u044F \u043B\u0443\u043D\u0430 \u0438 \u0433\u0440\u043E\u043C",
        "Client": "\u0425\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0448\u043E \u043E\u0434\u0435\u0442\u044B\u0439 \u044E\u043D\u043E\u0448\u0430",
        "Description": "\u0421\u0442\u043E\u0438\u043B\u043E \u043C\u043E\u0438\u043C \u043E\u0445\u0440\u0430\u043D\u043D\u0438\u043A\u0430\u043C\r\n\u0443\u0441\u043B\u044B\u0448\u0430\u0442\u044C, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u0437\u0434\u0435\u0441\u044C \u0432\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044F\r\n\u0417\u0438\u043D\u043E\u0433\u0440, \u043A\u0430\u043A \u043E\u043D\u0438 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0443\u0441\u0438\u043B\u0438. \u041D\u043E\r\n\u043C\u043D\u0435 \u0432 \u043B\u044E\u0431\u043E\u043C \u0441\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0435 \u043D\u0430\u0434\u043E \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0439\u0442\u0438\r\n\u0447\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0437 \u041B\u0435\u0441. \u041F\u043E\u0442\u043E\u043C\u0443 \u044F \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0448\u0443\r\n\u0442\u0435\u0431\u044F, \u043E\u043A\u0430\u0436\u0438 \u043F\u043E\u043C\u043E\u0449\u044C,\r\n\u0443\u0431\u0435\u0439 \u044D\u0442\u043E \u0447\u0443\u0434\u0438\u0449\u0435.",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0417\u0438\u043D\u043E\u0433\u0440\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
